https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/owGw0bARdE0YbjnrXHFNAJrfnBR.jpg Comedy performance from popular Irish stand-up Brendan Grace. Grace, now celebrating 40 years as an entertainer, was originally a musician, but when his band was struggling in the face of a hostile crowd he took to the stage solo and found his true vocation. He has since become known for his character sketches and humorous take on everyday life. Brendan Grace: It's A Great Laugh
